Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}譯者：白　字幕：chiman　影片：風之殤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——and she said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若逆来顺受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是不适合自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是自己所无法承认的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若全盘接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不会受伤

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要处处抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是合适自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是自己所承认的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要处处抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会遍体鳞伤

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两颗心空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有肯定否定两个极端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中 空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中 有我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,                      /伽蓝之洞

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽蓝之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1996年3月

Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识为JCS三位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触诊测得血压60
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保输液通路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上心电图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪小姐 能听到吗 两仪小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 陪同人员请在此等候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通路确保
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血压低 但其他方面情况稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交叉配血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插管完毕 进行术前处理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪小姐 要剪开您的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出血量好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多准备血包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是

Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无穷 无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下来是腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是… 死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了 干也君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 苍崎所长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您和通电话时的感觉不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干这一行 有时需要随机应变哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个简单魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过控制视野来切换性格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是在自抬身价么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在隐藏本性？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任君想像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫 快来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪小姐 两仪小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪小姐 感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种病例很罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但意识能够恢复真是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把一下脉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据精密检查的结果制定复健计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先联系家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪小姐恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她本人刚醒来不久 有些混乱

Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢绝亲属以外的面会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要来新的心理咨询师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荒耶老师的继任者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是个和蔼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是负责那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的眼睛已经不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还不至于失明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说正在渐渐恢复平静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小狗君也快能见她了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个小狗君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足足两年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他等了足足两年嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有人那样对我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是语言治疗师 苍崎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病房在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我还以为你会很消瘦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤光泽还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了你的事以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了柳树下的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我喜欢的类型 运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是语言治疗师 苍崎橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你治疗失语症
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说我是失语症
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是误诊 你只是嫌麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你出事伤到了脑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会被认为是失语症
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点一分钟就失业了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是大夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我的本业是魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要变戏法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心里的空洞不是魔术师能填补的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有普通人才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里的空洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是 孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来说这个还早了些 今天就到此为止

Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见 拜

Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 暂时没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫暂时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 橙子小姐…

Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是 孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不存在生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不该见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我 进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 很美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类却 如此孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把这个转交给两仪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称治疗师的女性每天都来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉间 和她的对话已经成了我的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 织君并不是没有肉体主导权
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是没有行使它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重人格有什么有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才不是双重人格那么简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各有各的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动还是统一的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种复杂离奇的人格别无他例
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应当称之为复合个别人格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复合个别人格？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但我还是有点疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是复合个别人格的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织君就没必要沉睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来他好像一直在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他的名字 回忆不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸间是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如洞一般空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无论怎样对自身没有实感 她还是两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说现在还没有把握生的实感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她早晚也会认识到自己是式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇生来注定是蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算培育的土壤和水分有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会长成另一种花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 空洞里总要填入点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而只能积累现在 形成新的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有帮手 只能凭自己再造伽蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句话 你只要像先前那样对待她就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 既然失去了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记忆中欠缺的部分已经无法追回了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式和两年前的杀人魔有何瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相已经石沉大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但织君没有理由消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他只要任由事态发展 消失的就是式你了

Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么主动选择了消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说剪刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有前科在先 严禁携带刀具入内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你为什么要剪刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想剪头发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去找美容师来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了庆祝你的康复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会找个行家来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人碰到我的头发 我想都不愿想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天起 可能会换人来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的恢复力还真是惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了 明天就能出院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪小姐 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于眼睛 明早拆绷带 今天一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再看那种世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再坠入那片黑暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太冲动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直死之魔眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍掉它太可惜了 式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把眼睛毁掉 该看到的还是会看到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想教你如何使用眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万物皆有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有完美的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.67,0:23:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都有接受破坏重建的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为两年前的事故 你的眼睛能够看到这些破绽了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到我们无法辨认的线并且长期接触死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑理解了它的含义 结果 就能看到死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 应该也能碰触它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你也该醒醒了 两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:24:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就是我这边的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要梦想能理所当然地得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要梦想能过上常人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有生存的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.07,0:24:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为心里空空如也吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解失去织后 你会感觉自己像变了一个人而重生

Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.55,0:24:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你明明没有活下去的意志 却还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.04,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有活下去的理由 却还害怕死

Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不从生死间选择其一 而只游走于境界边缘

Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.88,0:24:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪心会空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.42,0:24:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在那不懂装懂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.68,0:24:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因心中有机可乘 所以才会为这种程度的接触而动摇

Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.05,0:25:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于漂浮在这所医院里的杂念来说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体正是无上的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.05,0:25:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若再不醒醒 就会被它们附体而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.98,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.27,0:25:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.18,0:25:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若那能填补我内心的空洞 我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.16,0:25:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 如尼的守护还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.88,0:25:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来请自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.45,0:25:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 织君真的白死了吗 两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.23,0:25:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织君真的白死了吗 两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.97,0:26:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我 进去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.35,0:26:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空洞里总要填入点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.28,0:26:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而只能积累现在 形成新的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.90,0:26:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有帮手 只能凭自己再造伽蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.47,0:26:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句话 你只要像先前那样对待她就好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.26,0:27:22.48,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I'm singing in the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.17,0:27:26.57,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Just singing in the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.42,0:27:31.45,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}What a glorious feelin'
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.57,0:27:35.51,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I'm happy again
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.08,0:27:39.79,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I'm laughing at clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.43,0:27:44.17,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}So dark up above
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.59,0:27:48.69,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}The sun's in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.81,0:27:53.04,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}And I'm ready for love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.37,0:27:58.07,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Let the stormy clouds chase
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.60,0:28:02.26,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Everyone from the place
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.42,0:28:07.86,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Come on with the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.01,0:28:12.78,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I've a smile on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.05,0:28:16.68,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I walk down the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.26,0:28:20.36,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}With a happy refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.54,0:28:23.84,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Just singin',
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.39,0:28:26.90,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Singin' in the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:30.24,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Dancin' in the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.27,0:28:33.58,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Dee-ah dee-ah dee-ah
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.35,0:28:37.88,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}Dee-ah dee-ah dee-ah
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.72,0:28:42.11,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I'm happy again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.24,0:28:50.93,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I'm singin' I'm dancin' in the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.26,0:28:58.75,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,300)}I'm dancin' and singin' in the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.12,0:28:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织君真的白死了吗 两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.13,0:28:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.60,0:28:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 死是如此孤独 毫无价值
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.39,0:28:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死是如此黑暗 令人恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.61,0:28:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 比什么都可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.95,0:28:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.17,0:28:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要坠入那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.31,0:29:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此简单的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.70,0:29:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳 你是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.14,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.31,0:29:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.42,0:29:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在病房设了结界 令灵体无法进入
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.67,0:29:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到它们会为了破除结界而获取肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.21,0:29:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按理说 它们是没有这么聪明的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.87,0:29:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我失误了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.68,0:29:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就想个办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.92,0:29:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.98,0:30:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fehu uruz thurisaz
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.94,0:30:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手头的Ansuz不够强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.22,0:30:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你这个大骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.10,0:30:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种的比较棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.94,0:30:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若对方活着 烧掉心脏就行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但死者却没这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.55,0:30:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为死了 少条胳膊少个头都无关痛痒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.68,0:30:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要媲美火葬场的火力 或者找个高僧来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.54,0:30:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在那强调理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.26,0:30:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了 你杀不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.86,0:30:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也杀不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者已矣 无法再杀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们暂时撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.55,0:30:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它是不是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.16,0:30:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是具「活尸体」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.20,0:31:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.29,0:31:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管它是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.77,0:31:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会杀给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.04,0:31:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.62,0:32:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.33,0:32:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行尸走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.69,0:32:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在我面前现眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.31,0:33:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后关头掉以轻心了吗 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.50,0:33:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.51,0:33:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀掉软弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.76,0:33:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会把…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.32,0:33:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式交给你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.21,0:34:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.51,0:34:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.19,0:34:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要教我如何使用眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.19,0:34:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.47,0:34:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会教你如何使用直死
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.98,0:34:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要帮我工作作为报答
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.69,0:34:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.32,0:34:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正缺个左右手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.77,0:34:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那能杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.23,0:34:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.60,0:34:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我干
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.80,0:34:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.12,0:34:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也没有其他目的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.71,0:35:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有目的吗 真悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.96,0:35:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.12,0:35:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然空空如也 就能填入任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.04,0:35:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.97,0:35:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪去找更好的未来啊

Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.44,0:35:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他消失了 由此换来了什么 又守护了什么呢

Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.20,0:35:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经消失的织
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.80,0:35:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是为了守护自己的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.58,0:35:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福生活的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.17,0:35:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只给我留下了深深的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.34,0:36:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中意你 近期再会吧 黑桐…


Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.70,0:36:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 式
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.86,0:36:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.96,0:36:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你… 一直在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.25,0:36:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你… 一直在保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.65,0:36:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐干也
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.00,0:36:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个法国诗人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.59,0:36:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晴了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.59,0:37:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是个出院的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来有些东西 是不会失去的

Dialogue: 1,0:37:31.48,0:37:35.72,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}夢の欠片
