Dialogue: 1,0:38:00.37,0:38:05.60,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}一つ消えて
Dialogue: 1,0:38:06.22,0:38:17.18,edjpn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}夜明けのアリアが響いた
