Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.21,0:42:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是巫条雾绘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.33,0:42:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是… 父亲的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.31,0:42:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为实现你的愿望而来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.01,0:42:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能获得自由的另一具身体 不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.97,0:42:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是… 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.80,0:43:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 这样没法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.23,0:43:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.45,0:43:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是浅上藤乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.39,0:43:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被治愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.01,0:43:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.15,0:43:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来治愈你身体的异常
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.21,0:43:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是… 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.10,0:43:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是… 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.49,0:43:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.05,0:43:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒耶宗莲

Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.65,0:44:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不能容忍你的存在罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.57,0:44:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.82,0:44:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.73,0:44:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐 你知道茅见滨的小川公寓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.38,0:44:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小川公寓是两座半月形十层大厦相邻而建的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.92,0:44:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.77,0:44:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去拜访原应死去的家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.07,0:44:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.76,0:44:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着才有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.54,0:44:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去确认一下不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.64,0:44:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直视那片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.99,0:44:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后忆起汝之真名
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.19,0:44:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把式怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.73,0:44:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太极是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.25,0:44:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了融入太极的太极的具现…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.48,0:44:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.58,0:44:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.87,0:45:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条螺旋 若是矛盾的就好了
